  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1129720/extras/081623347770cf8c018850a4fff2921b.webp?t=1753792631\" width=300 height=59 /></span><br><strong>Area 51 Defense</strong> is an action-packed survival shooter with a deadly arsenal, monstrous enemies and explosive action!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1129720/extras/f588706a868faf2fc7aa1e1925b9be72.webp?t=1753792631\" width=300 height=59 /></span><br>Mysterious forces are amassing near the air force base of Area 51. <br>You are a lone soldier fending off these supernatural invaders. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1129720/extras/aec012792813e4e991c55180975cc9e6.webp?t=1753792631\" width=300 height=60 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Use an arsenal of 8 deadly weapons<br></li><li> Eliminate various monsters and mutants<br></li><li> Get kill streaks and special combos<br></li><li> Discover different power-ups to help your survival<br></li><li> Shoot the gas bottles to create a trap for the invaders<br></li><li> Experiment with the in-built level editor<br></li><li> Gain the highest score and climb up the Steam Leaderboards<br></li><li> And try to survive as many waves as you can!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1129720/extras/904a0121c68da9d25ae5202cb96bef16.webp?t=1753792631\" width=400 height=31 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1129720/extras/f3f197a8bf917e96043314c8b0acab15.avif?t=1753792631\" width=500 height=158 /></span><br><br>For all the players looking for new releases from <strong>GameRealmMadness </strong>- <strong>ENEMY REMAINS</strong> is a punishing and action-packed continuation to Kalaban, with all new frights, foes and horrors. Available now on Steam Early Access! <br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1129720/extras/904a0121c68da9d25ae5202cb96bef16.webp?t=1753792631\" width=400 height=31 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1129720/extras/081623347770cf8c018850a4fff2921b.webp?t=1753792631\" width=300 height=59 /></span><br><strong>Area 51 Defense</strong> is an action-packed survival shooter with a deadly arsenal, monstrous enemies and explosive action!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1129720/extras/f588706a868faf2fc7aa1e1925b9be72.webp?t=1753792631\" width=300 height=59 /></span><br>Mysterious forces are amassing near the air force base of Area 51. <br>You are a lone soldier fending off these supernatural invaders. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1129720/extras/aec012792813e4e991c55180975cc9e6.webp?t=1753792631\" width=300 height=60 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Use an arsenal of 8 deadly weapons<br></li><li> Eliminate various monsters and mutants<br></li><li> Get kill streaks and special combos<br></li><li> Discover different power-ups to help your survival<br></li><li> Shoot the gas bottles to create a trap for the invaders<br></li><li> Experiment with the in-built level editor<br></li><li> Gain the highest score and climb up the Steam Leaderboards<br></li><li> And try to survive as many waves as you can!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1129720/extras/904a0121c68da9d25ae5202cb96bef16.webp?t=1753792631\" width=400 height=31 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1129720/extras/f3f197a8bf917e96043314c8b0acab15.avif?t=1753792631\" width=500 height=158 /></span><br><br>For all the players looking for new releases from <strong>GameRealmMadness </str